```plantuml
@startuml dowjones_hammer
actor User
participant SlackBot
participant REST_API
participant InitiationLambda
participant SNS
participant IdentificationLambda
participant DynamoDB
participant JIRA
participant EC2
participant AWS_Resources

User -> SlackBot: Request security scan
SlackBot -> REST_API: Trigger scan
REST_API -> InitiationLambda: Start process
InitiationLambda -> SNS: Publish scan event
SNS -> IdentificationLambda: Invoke security checks
loop For each AWS resource
    IdentificationLambda -> AWS_Resources: Check security configuration
    AWS_Resources --> IdentificationLambda: Return resource state
    IdentificationLambda -> DynamoDB: Store issue details
end
IdentificationLambda --> EC2: Send results
EC2 -> JIRA: Create tickets for issues
EC2 -> SlackBot: Send notifications
SlackBot --> User: Notify scan completion
@enduml
```